## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
Sometimes, and empty field or a zero is indicating a missing value. But is that really unique? Could there be valid empty or zero fields? Has the convention for missing values been made explicit somewhere?
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
有時候，空欄位或數值 0 會被用來表示缺失值。但這樣的表示方式真的具有唯一性嗎？是否也可能存在有效的空欄位或值為 0 的欄位？對於缺失值的表示慣例，是否已在某處明確說明？
~~~
